<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ قَالَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٦٩١ - نا مَعْمَرٌ ,<span class="c5"> عَنْ قَتَادَةَ فِي قَوْلِهِ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{عَلَى فَتْرَةٍ مِنَ الرُّسُلِ}</span> <span class="c4">[المائدة: ١٩]</span> ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«كَانَ بَيْنَ عِيسَى , وَمُحَمَّدٍ خَمْسُمِائَةِ سَنَةٍ وَسِتُّونَ سَنَةً»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٦٩٢ - قَالَ مَعْمَرٌ ,<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ الْكَلْبِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">«خَمْسُمِائَةِ سَنَةٍ وَأَرْبَعُونَ سَنَةً»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>